### ============================================================================
### PAYMENTS (Flutterwave) — /api/v1/payments
### ============================================================================

### Initiate payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/initiate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "currency": "NGN",
  "customerEmail": "dikethomas@example.com",
  "customerName": "Dike Thomas",
  "description": "Credit purchase - 50 credits",
  "txRef": "{{txRef}}",
  "customerPhone": "+2348012345678",
  "redirectUrl": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/callback"
}

### Verify transaction by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/verify/{{txRef}}

### Verify transaction by reference
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/verify-by-reference/{{txRef}}

### Refund transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/refund/{{txRef}}

### Flutterwave webhook handler
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/webhook/flutterwave
Content-Type: application/json
verif-hash: your-webhook-secret-hash

{
  "event": "charge.completed",
  "data": {
    "tx_ref": "{{txRef}}",
    "flw_ref": "FLW-REF-123",
    "status": "successful",
    "amount": 5000
  }
}

### Get payment config
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/config

### Generate transaction reference
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/generate-reference


### ============================================================================
### CREDIT PURCHASES — /api/v1/credit-purchases
### ============================================================================

### Initiate credit purchase
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-purchases/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "credits": 50,
  "currency": "NGN"
}

### Verify purchase
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-purchases/verify/{{txRef}}?transaction_id=

### Payment callback
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-purchases/callback?tx_ref={{txRef}}&status=successful

### Purchase history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-purchases/history
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get purchase by txRef
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-purchases/{{txRef}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
